{"title":"唱支歌儿朋友听","authors":["王老九"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":4,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱支歌儿朋友听"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王老九"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳春四月桃花盛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"首都北京春更浓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十六届乒乓赛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐我老汉唱几声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家户户多欢腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六亿人民重友情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声迎来远道客，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宾主欢绣五彩虹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五洲健儿临北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卅树花儿朵朵红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"球坛老将威风在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抢锦夺标看新生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我国队员年纪轻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"借鞭策己取真经，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发展体育强体质，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设祖国立功勋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"体育使者结亲朋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拧成钢绳保和平，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风遍拂五洲地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界处处太阳红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远在千里心情动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似闻乒乓触案声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伴着朋友雄姿舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱支歌儿朋友听。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1961年4月4日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陕西临潼"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}